msgid "The cherry on the sunday is, one more time, we replaced [1306 lines of clear and structured code](https://github.com/darktable-org/darktable/blob/darktable-3.6.x/src/gui/accelerators.c) by a [monstruosity of close to 4400 lines](https://github.com/darktable-org/darktable/blob/darktable-4.2.x/src/gui/accelerators.c), with gems like :\n"
msgstr "A cereja do bolo é que, mais uma vez, substituímos [1306 linhas de código claro e estruturado](https://github.com/darktable-org/darktable/blob/darktable-3.6.x/src/gui/accelerators.c) por uma [monstruosidade de quase 4400 linhas](https://github.com/darktable-org/darktable/blob/darktable-4.2.x/src/gui/accelerators.c), com pérolas como:\n"

